#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:292
msgid ""
"**PAUSE_MODE_INHERIT** = **0** --- Inherits pause mode from the node's "
"parent. For the root node, it is equivalent to :ref:`PAUSE_MODE_STOP "
"<class_Node_constant_PAUSE_MODE_STOP>`. Default."
msgstr ""
"**PAUSE_MODE_INHERIT** = **0** —— 从节点的父级继承暂停模式。对于根节点，它等效于 "
":ref:`PAUSE_MODE_STOP <class_Node_constant_PAUSE_MODE_STOP>`。默认。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:294
msgid ""
"**PAUSE_MODE_STOP** = **1** --- Stops processing when the :ref:`SceneTree"
" <class_SceneTree>` is paused."
msgstr ""
"**PAUSE_MODE_STOP** = **1** —— 当 :ref:`SceneTree <class_SceneTree>` "
"暂停时，停止处理。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:296
msgid ""
"**PAUSE_MODE_PROCESS** = **2** --- Continue to process regardless of the "
":ref:`SceneTree <class_SceneTree>` pause state."
msgstr ""
"**PAUSE_MODE_PROCESS** = **2** —— 继续处理，无论 :ref:`SceneTree "
"<class_SceneTree>` 暂停状态如何。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:310
