#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:314
msgid "**DUPLICATE_GROUPS** = **2** --- Duplicate the node's groups."
msgstr "**DUPLICATE_GROUPS** = **2** —— 复制节点的编组。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:316
