#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:385
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_ENTER_TREE** = **10** --- Notification received when the "
"node enters a :ref:`SceneTree <class_SceneTree>`."
msgstr ""
"**NOTIFICATION_ENTER_TREE** = **10** —— 节点进入 :ref:`SceneTree "
"<class_SceneTree>` 时收到的通知。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:387
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_EXIT_TREE** = **11** --- Notification received when the "
"node is about to exit a :ref:`SceneTree <class_SceneTree>`."
msgstr ""
"**NOTIFICATION_EXIT_TREE** = **11** —— 当节点即将退出 :ref:`SceneTree "
"<class_SceneTree>` 时收到通知。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:389
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_MOVED_IN_PARENT** = **12** --- Notification received when "
"the node is moved in the parent."
msgstr "**NOTIFICATION_MOVED_IN_PARENT** = **12** —— 当节点在父节点中移动时收到通知。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:391
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_READY** = **13** --- Notification received when the node "
"is ready. See :ref:`_ready <class_Node_method__ready>`."
msgstr ""
"**NOTIFICATION_READY** = **13** —— 节点准备就绪时收到通知。参见 :ref:`_ready "
"<class_Node_method__ready>`。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:393
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_PAUSED** = **14** --- Notification received when the node "
"is paused."
msgstr "**NOTIFICATION_PAUSED** = **14** —— 节点暂停时收到通知。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:395
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_UNPAUSED** = **15** --- Notification received when the "
"node is unpaused."
msgstr "**NOTIFICATION_UNPAUSED** = **15** —— 节点取消暂停时收到通知。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:397
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_PHYSICS_PROCESS** = **16** --- Notification received every"
" frame when the physics process flag is set (see "
":ref:`set_physics_process <class_Node_method_set_physics_process>`)."
msgstr ""
"**NOTIFICATION_PHYSICS_PROCESS** = **16** —— 当设置了物理过程标记时，每帧都会收到通知（请参阅 "
":ref:`set_physics_process <class_Node_method_set_physics_process>`）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:399
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_PROCESS** = **17** --- Notification received every frame "
"when the process flag is set (see :ref:`set_process "
"<class_Node_method_set_process>`)."
msgstr ""
"**NOTIFICATION_PROCESS** = **17** —— 当设置了处理标志时，每帧都会收到通知（请参阅 "
":ref:`set_process <class_Node_method_set_process>`）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:401
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_PARENTED** = **18** --- Notification received when a node "
"is set as a child of another node."
msgstr "**NOTIFICATION_PARENTED** = **18** —— 当一个节点，设置为另一个节点的子节点时，收到通知。"

