#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:581
msgid ""
"Called when the node enters the :ref:`SceneTree <class_SceneTree>` (e.g. "
"upon instancing, scene changing, or after calling :ref:`add_child "
"<class_Node_method_add_child>` in a script). If the node has children, "
"its :ref:`_enter_tree <class_Node_method__enter_tree>` callback will be "
"called first, and then that of the children."
msgstr ""
"当节点进入 :ref:`SceneTree <class_SceneTree>` （例如实例化、场景更改、或在脚本中调用 "
":ref:`add_child <class_Node_method_add_child>` 之后）时调用。如果节点有子节点，则将首先调用其 "
":ref:`_enter_tree <class_Node_method__enter_tree>` 回调，然后再调用子节点的回调。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:583
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the :ref:`NOTIFICATION_ENTER_TREE "
"<class_Node_constant_NOTIFICATION_ENTER_TREE>` notification in "
":ref:`Object._notification <class_Object_method__notification>`."
msgstr ""
"对应于 :ref:`Object._notification <class_Object_method__notification>` 中的 "
":ref:`NOTIFICATION_ENTER_TREE "
"<class_Node_constant_NOTIFICATION_ENTER_TREE>` 通知。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:589
msgid "void **_exit_tree** **(** **)** virtual"
msgstr "void **_exit_tree** **(** **)** virtual"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:591
msgid ""
"Called when the node is about to leave the :ref:`SceneTree "
"<class_SceneTree>` (e.g. upon freeing, scene changing, or after calling "
":ref:`remove_child <class_Node_method_remove_child>` in a script). If the"
" node has children, its :ref:`_exit_tree <class_Node_method__exit_tree>` "
"callback will be called last, after all its children have left the tree."
msgstr ""
"当节点即将离开 :ref:`SceneTree <class_SceneTree>` 时调用（例如，在释放、更改场景、或在脚本中调用 "
":ref:`remove_child <class_Node_method_remove_child>` "
"之后）。如果节点有子节点，则它的所有子节点都离开树后，将最后调用它的 :ref:`_exit_tree "
"<class_Node_method__exit_tree>` 回调。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:593
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the :ref:`NOTIFICATION_EXIT_TREE "
"<class_Node_constant_NOTIFICATION_EXIT_TREE>` notification in "
":ref:`Object._notification <class_Object_method__notification>` and "
"signal :ref:`tree_exiting <class_Node_signal_tree_exiting>`. To get "
"notified when the node has already left the active tree, connect to the "
":ref:`tree_exited <class_Node_signal_tree_exited>`."
msgstr ""
"对应于 :ref:`Object._notification <class_Object_method__notification>` 中的 "
":ref:`NOTIFICATION_EXIT_TREE "
"<class_Node_constant_NOTIFICATION_EXIT_TREE>` 通知，和 :ref:`tree_exiting "
"<class_Node_signal_tree_exiting>` 信号。要在节点已经离开活动树时得到通知，请连接到 "
":ref:`tree_exited <class_Node_signal_tree_exited>`"

