#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:611
msgid ""
"void **_input** **(** :ref:`InputEvent <class_InputEvent>` event **)** "
"virtual"
msgstr ""
"void **_input** **(** :ref:`InputEvent <class_InputEvent>` event **)** "
"virtual"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:613
msgid ""
"Called when there is an input event. The input event propagates up "
"through the node tree until a node consumes it."
msgstr "有输入事件时调用。输入事件在节点树中向上传播，直到一个节点将其消耗为止。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:615
msgid ""
"It is only called if input processing is enabled, which is done "
"automatically if this method is overridden, and can be toggled with "
":ref:`set_process_input <class_Node_method_set_process_input>`."
msgstr ""
"仅在启用输入处理的情况下才调用它，如果此方法被重写，它将自动完成启用，并且可以使用 :ref:`set_process_input "
"<class_Node_method_set_process_input>` 来切换。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:617
#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:669
#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:683
msgid ""
"To consume the input event and stop it propagating further to other "
"nodes, :ref:`SceneTree.set_input_as_handled "
"<class_SceneTree_method_set_input_as_handled>` can be called."
msgstr ""
"为了消耗输入事件并停止它传播到其他节点，可以调用 :ref:`SceneTree.set_input_as_handled "
"<class_SceneTree_method_set_input_as_handled>`。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:619
msgid ""
"For gameplay input, :ref:`_unhandled_input "
"<class_Node_method__unhandled_input>` and :ref:`_unhandled_key_input "
"<class_Node_method__unhandled_key_input>` are usually a better fit as "
"they allow the GUI to intercept the events first."
msgstr ""
"对于游戏输入，通常 :ref:`_unhandled_input <class_Node_method__unhandled_input>` 和 "
":ref:`_unhandled_key_input <class_Node_method__unhandled_key_input>` "
"比较合适，因为它们允许GUI首先截获事件。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:625
msgid ""
"void **_physics_process** **(** :ref:`float <class_float>` delta **)** "
"virtual"
msgstr ""
"void **_physics_process** **(** :ref:`float <class_float>` delta **)** "
"virtual"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:627
msgid ""
"Called during the physics processing step of the main loop. Physics "
"processing means that the frame rate is synced to the physics, i.e. the "
"``delta`` variable should be constant."
msgstr "在主循环的物理处理步骤中调用。物理处理意味着将帧速率同步到物理上，即 ``delta`` 变量应为常数。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:629
msgid ""
"It is only called if physics processing is enabled, which is done "
"automatically if this method is overridden, and can be toggled with "
":ref:`set_physics_process <class_Node_method_set_physics_process>`."
msgstr ""
"仅在启用了物理处理的情况下才调用它，如果此方法被重写，它将自动完成启用，并且可以使用 :ref:`set_physics_process "
"<class_Node_method_set_physics_process>` 进行切换。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:631
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the :ref:`NOTIFICATION_PHYSICS_PROCESS "
"<class_Node_constant_NOTIFICATION_PHYSICS_PROCESS>` notification in "
":ref:`Object._notification <class_Object_method__notification>`."
msgstr ""
"对应于 :ref:`Object._notification <class_Object_method__notification>` 中的 "
":ref:`NOTIFICATION_PHYSICS_PROCESS "
"<class_Node_constant_NOTIFICATION_PHYSICS_PROCESS>` 通知。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:637
msgid "void **_process** **(** :ref:`float <class_float>` delta **)** virtual"
msgstr "void **_process** **(** :ref:`float <class_float>` delta **)** virtual"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:639
msgid ""
"Called during the processing step of the main loop. Processing happens at"
" every frame and as fast as possible, so the ``delta`` time since the "
"previous frame is not constant."
msgstr "在主循环的处理步骤中调用。处理发生在每个帧上并尽可能快，因此自上一帧以来的 ``delta`` 时间不是恒定的。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:641
msgid ""
"It is only called if processing is enabled, which is done automatically "
