#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:727
msgid ""
"Adds the node to a group. Groups are helpers to name and organize a "
"subset of nodes, for example \"enemies\" or \"collectables\". A node can "
"be in any number of groups. Nodes can be assigned a group at any time, "
"but will not be added until they are inside the scene tree (see "
":ref:`is_inside_tree <class_Node_method_is_inside_tree>`). See notes in "
"the description, and the group methods in :ref:`SceneTree "
"<class_SceneTree>`."
msgstr ""
"将节点添加到编组。编组是命名和组织节点子集的助手，例如 ``敌人`` 或 "
"``收藏品``。一个节点可以处于任意数量的编组中。可以在任何时候为节点分配一个组，但是直到它们在场景树中时，才被添加（请参见 "
":ref:`is_inside_tree <class_Node_method_is_inside_tree>`）。请参阅说明中的注释，以及 "
":ref:`SceneTree <class_SceneTree>` 中的编组方法。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:729
