"on this node and recursively on all its children. If the ``parent_first``"
" argument is ``true``, the method will be called on the current node "
"first, then on all its children. If ``parent_first`` is ``false``, the "
"children will be called first."
msgstr ""
"在此节点上，使用 ``args`` 中给出的参数，调用给定方法（如果存在），并在其所有子节点上递归调用。如果 ``parent_first`` "
"参数为 ``true``，则将首先在当前节点上调用该方法，然后在其所有子节点上调用该方法。如果 ``parent_first`` 为 "
"``false``，则首先调用子级。"

