#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1149
msgid ""
"Queues a node for deletion at the end of the current frame. When deleted,"
" all of its child nodes will be deleted as well. This method ensures it's"
" safe to delete the node, contrary to :ref:`Object.free "
"<class_Object_method_free>`. Use :ref:`Object.is_queued_for_deletion "
"<class_Object_method_is_queued_for_deletion>` to check whether a node "
"will be deleted at the end of the frame."
