#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1157
msgid ""
"Moves this node to the bottom of parent node's children hierarchy. This "
"is often useful in GUIs (:ref:`Control <class_Control>` nodes), because "
"their order of drawing depends on their order in the tree, i.e. the "
"further they are on the node list, the higher they are drawn. After using"
" ``raise``, a Control will be drawn on top of their siblings."
msgstr ""
"将此节点移到父节点的子层次结构的底部。这在GUI（:ref:`Control <class_Control>` "
"节点）中通常很有用，因为它们的绘制顺序取决于它们在树中的顺序，即它们在节点列表中的位置越远，绘制的位置就越高。使用 ``raise`` "
"后，``Control`` 将被绘制在其同级之上。"

