":ref:`NOTIFICATION_PHYSICS_PROCESS "
"<class_Node_constant_NOTIFICATION_PHYSICS_PROCESS>` at a fixed (usually "
"60 FPS, see :ref:`Engine.iterations_per_second "
"<class_Engine_property_iterations_per_second>` to change) interval (and "
"the :ref:`_physics_process <class_Node_method__physics_process>` callback"
" will be called if exists). Enabled automatically if "
":ref:`_physics_process <class_Node_method__physics_process>` is "
"overridden. Any calls to this before :ref:`_ready "
"<class_Node_method__ready>` will be ignored."
msgstr ""
"启用或禁用物理（即固定帧频）处理。在处理节点时，它将以固定的（通常为60 FPS，参见 :ref:`Engine.target_fps "
"<class_Engine_property_target_fps>` 以更改）间隔（如果存在的话，将会调用 "
":ref:`_physics_process <class_Node_method__physics_process>` 回调）来接收一个 "
":ref:`NOTIFICATION_PHYSICS_PROCESS "
"<class_Node_constant_NOTIFICATION_PHYSICS_PROCESS>`。如果 "
":ref:`_physics_process <class_Node_method__physics_process>` "
"被重写，则自动启用。:ref:`_ready <class_Node_method__ready>` 之前，任何对此的调用，将被忽略。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1309
msgid ""
"void **set_physics_process_internal** **(** :ref:`bool <class_bool>` "
"enable **)**"
msgstr ""
"void **set_physics_process_internal** **(** :ref:`bool <class_bool>` "
"enable **)**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1311
msgid ""
"Enables or disables internal physics for this node. Internal physics "
"processing happens in isolation from the normal :ref:`_physics_process "
"<class_Node_method__physics_process>` calls and is used by some nodes "
"internally to guarantee proper functioning even if the node is paused or "
"physics processing is disabled for scripting (:ref:`set_physics_process "
"<class_Node_method_set_physics_process>`). Only useful for advanced uses "
"to manipulate built-in nodes' behaviour."
msgstr ""
"启用或禁用此节点的内部物理。内部物理处理独立于普通的 :ref:`_physics_process "
"<class_Node_method__physics_process>` "
"调用发生，并且即使节点暂停或为编写脚本禁用了物理处理（:ref:`set_physics_process "
"<class_Node_method_set_physics_process>`），某些节点内部也使用内部物理来保证其功能正常。仅对用于操纵内置节点行为的高级用途有用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1317
msgid "void **set_process** **(** :ref:`bool <class_bool>` enable **)**"
msgstr "void **set_process** **(** :ref:`bool <class_bool>` enable **)**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1319
msgid ""
"Enables or disables processing. When a node is being processed, it will "
"receive a :ref:`NOTIFICATION_PROCESS "
"<class_Node_constant_NOTIFICATION_PROCESS>` on every drawn frame (and the"
" :ref:`_process <class_Node_method__process>` callback will be called if "
"exists). Enabled automatically if :ref:`_process "
"<class_Node_method__process>` is overridden. Any calls to this before "
":ref:`_ready <class_Node_method__ready>` will be ignored."
msgstr ""
"启用或禁用处理。处理节点时，它将在每个绘制的帧上收到一个 :ref:`NOTIFICATION_PROCESS "
"<class_Node_constant_NOTIFICATION_PROCESS>` （如果存在，则将调用 :ref:`_process "
"<class_Node_method__process>` 回调）。如果 :ref:`_process "
"<class_Node_method__process>` 被重写，则自动启用。:ref:`_ready "
"<class_Node_method__ready>` 之前，任何对此的调用，将被忽略。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1325
msgid "void **set_process_input** **(** :ref:`bool <class_bool>` enable **)**"
msgstr "void **set_process_input** **(** :ref:`bool <class_bool>` enable **)**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1327
msgid ""
"Enables or disables input processing. This is not required for GUI "
"controls! Enabled automatically if :ref:`_input "
"<class_Node_method__input>` is overridden. Any calls to this before "
":ref:`_ready <class_Node_method__ready>` will be ignored."
msgstr ""
"启用或禁用输入处理。GUI控件不需要此函数！如果 :ref:`_input <class_Node_method__input>` "
"被重写，则自动启用。:ref:`_ready <class_Node_method__ready>` 之前，任何对此的调用，将被忽略。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1333
msgid "void **set_process_internal** **(** :ref:`bool <class_bool>` enable **)**"
msgstr "void **set_process_internal** **(** :ref:`bool <class_bool>` enable **)**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1335
msgid ""
"Enables or disabled internal processing for this node. Internal "
"processing happens in isolation from the normal :ref:`_process "
"<class_Node_method__process>` calls and is used by some nodes internally "
"to guarantee proper functioning even if the node is paused or processing "
"is disabled for scripting (:ref:`set_process "
"<class_Node_method_set_process>`). Only useful for advanced uses to "
"manipulate built-in nodes' behaviour."
msgstr ""
"启用或禁用此节点的内部处理。内部处理独立于正常的 :ref:`_process <class_Node_method__process>` "
"调用而发生，并且即使节点暂停或为编写脚本禁用了处理（:ref:`set_process "
"<class_Node_method_set_process>`），某些节点内部也使用内部处理来保证其功能正常。仅对用于操纵内置节点行为的高级用途有用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1341
msgid ""
"void **set_process_unhandled_input** **(** :ref:`bool <class_bool>` "
"enable **)**"
msgstr ""
"void **set_process_unhandled_input** **(** :ref:`bool <class_bool>` "
"enable **)**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1343
msgid ""
"Enables unhandled input processing. This is not required for GUI "
"controls! It enables the node to receive all input that was not "
"previously handled (usually by a :ref:`Control <class_Control>`). Enabled"
" automatically if :ref:`_unhandled_input "
"<class_Node_method__unhandled_input>` is overridden. Any calls to this "
"before :ref:`_ready <class_Node_method__ready>` will be ignored."
msgstr ""
"启用未处理的输入处理。GUI控件不需要此函数！它使节点能够接收，以前未处理（通常由一个 :ref:`Control "
"<class_Control>` 处理）的所有输入。如果 :ref:`_unhandled_input "
"<class_Node_method__unhandled_input>` 被重写，则自动启用。:ref:`_ready "
"<class_Node_method__ready>` 之前，任何对此的调用，将被忽略。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1349
