#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node.rst:1351
msgid ""
"Enables unhandled key input processing. Enabled automatically if "
":ref:`_unhandled_key_input <class_Node_method__unhandled_key_input>` is "
"overridden. Any calls to this before :ref:`_ready "
"<class_Node_method__ready>` will be ignored."
msgstr ""
"启用未处理的按键输入处理。如果 :ref:`_unhandled_key_input "
"<class_Node_method__unhandled_key_input>` 被重写，则自动启用。:ref:`_ready "
"<class_Node_method__ready>` 之前，任何对此的调用，将被忽略。"

